                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"Seal of the Montreal Literary Club\"><placeName>MONTREAL</placeName> LITERARY\n                CLUB<lb/> NUNC LIBRIS VETERUM NUNC SOMNO ET INERTIBUS HORIS</p>\n            <p rend=\"align(right)\">\n                <placeName>Montreal</placeName>\n                <date>13th August 5625</date>\n            </p>\n            <p>The <addressee>Rev. Isaac Leeser</addressee></p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(2)\">Dear Sir</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(4)\">I should have written<lb/> you ere this, but it was long<lb/> before\n                I could obtain a final reply<lb/> from the <persName>Rev Mr Hass</persName> who<lb/>\n                has concluded now not to take<lb/> the volumes of sermons, as the<lb/> price he says\n                is too high for him<lb/> and he was told he could get them<lb/> for two dollars.\n                Entre nous, <persName>Mr<lb/> Hass</persName> is at present too much<lb/> engaged\n                with manufacturing<lb/> vinegar, to cultivate pulpit eloquence<lb/> and as he has\n                lost nearly all<lb/> his best members, there may</p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p38p5vw65/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
