                  "type": "Annotation",
                  "motivation": "commenting",
                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>possibly exist another reason or<lb/> inducement less to invest. He<lb/> asked me\n                when he saw me to<lb/> request you to discontinue<lb/> sending him the Occident\n                because<lb/> “he did not order it.”</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">I am very much obliged<lb/> to you for sending me the missing<lb/>\n                numbers of the Occident. By<lb/> error however the number<lb/> 49 of vol 17 was sent\n                me for<lb/> no 49 of vol eighteen which<lb/> latter number I want. Will<lb/> you\n                please let me have it at<lb/> your convenience when my set<lb/> will be\n                complete.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">I hear that <persName>Mr<lb/> Samuel Benjamin</persName> is\n                about<lb/> visiting <placeName>Canada</placeName>—will probably</p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p38p5vw65/canvas/p2"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
