                  "id": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p38p5vw65/manifest/annotation/p3",
                  "type": "Annotation",
                  "motivation": "commenting",
                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>be here in three weeks. I will<lb/> not fail to remind him of his<lb/> indebtedness\n                to you.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">I leave town with my<lb/> family tomorrow for a few\n                weeks—<lb/>though I shall be here for <add>שבת</add>—and<lb/> having some\n                preparations to make<lb/> must close this now. Hoping you<lb/> are enjoying good\n                health and all<lb/> other pleasant things</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(4)\">I remain my dear Sir</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(5)\">yours truly</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(6)\">\n                <persName role=\"author\">Abraham de Sola</persName>\n            </p>\n        </body>\n    </text>\n</TEI>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p38p5vw65/canvas/p3"
                }
